Question 1️⃣ – Simple REST API

Using Spring Boot, write a REST API that returns:

Hello, Welcome to Spring Boot!

Requirements:

Create a controller

Use @RestController

Create a GET API endpoint /hello

Example request:

GET /hello

Expected response:

Hello, Welcome to Spring Boot!
-----
@RestController
public class HelloController{
    
    @GetMapping("/hello")
    public String sayHello()
    {
        return "Hello, Welcome to Spring Boot!";
    }
}
